b=i-j-k
i = \begin{pmatrix} 1 \\ 0 \\ 0\end{pmatrix}
j = \begin{pmatrix} 0 \\ 1 \\ 0\end{pmatrix}
k = \begin{pmatrix} 0 \\ 0 \\ 1\end{pmatrix}
b  =\begin{pmatrix} 1 \\ -1 \\ -1\end{pmatrix}.
\|b\| = \sqrt{1^2+(-1)^2+(-1)^2} = \sqrt{3}
5
b
\alpha
\|\alpha b\| = 5
\|\alpha b\| = |a|\|b\|
a
\vert ai-aj-ak\vert=5
